    public class RuleCacherDelegate
extends Object
implements RuleCacher, org.springframework.beans.factory.SmartInitializingSingleton, org.springframework.beans.factory.BeanFactoryAware
    RuleCacher delegate class that persists the rule to the configuration center when the rule configuration datasource implementation (such as nacosDataSource) is saved
